{
  "stem": "24830.2",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They started to-- you know, to try to get as many Jew as-- and the terrible thing is most of the people who came live in hotel.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Is that right?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Hotel.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they all have paper like me, with Jew in it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So what they did is they go to every hotel.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they say, [POINTING] paper.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And then they were you know, caught, and sent to deportation.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "First to a camp in-- I think in close to France-- close to Paris, transit.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And then they were deported.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So the way it all started, it-- I knew some young people from the youth hostel, when we go-- we went camping, and-- I knew some young people of my age and older.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And they decided to do something, you know, not to just to be a sitting duck-- something, something like this.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They decided to do something.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So the first thing to-- and they-- they ask me if I want to join them.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And you know, my parents were not too crazy, but they-- they let me.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So I work with a man, which were-- who had confidant-- because I was really shy.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And so he used to tell me, OK, you go to this hotel.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And you ask all these paper who have these big, you know, Jew on the the-- on their identification paper-- ask them for two picture and their name, you know.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then we'll-- the first thing was to make false paper.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because one false paper save a life.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "With good paper, you were saved.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] So that's what I did.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I went and get-- and then there was two people-- one, Pierre Muchnic, and I forget the other name.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They were in a studio, somewhere in hiding.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And that's all they did.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
